<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.9">
<l>naṅkaimīr nīrumor peṇpeṟṟu nalkiṉī</l>
<l>reṅṅaṉē collukēṉ yāṉpeṟṟa vēḻaiyai</l>
<l>caṅkeṉṉuñ cakkara meṉṉun tuḻāyeṉṉu</l>
<l>miṅṅaṉē collu mirāppaka leṉceykēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You ladies, you too have begotten [and] brought up a daughter.</l>
<l>How will I speak to the fool I got?</l>
<l>“The conch”, “the discus”, “the Tulsi”,</l>
<l>thus she speaks day [and] night. What will I do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
